  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC448">
        <l>koṭuveṉ kiḷavi paṭarkkai yāyiṉun</l>
      <l>taṉṉaip piṟaṉpōṟ kūṟuṅ kuṟippiṟ</l>
	<l>ṟaṉṉiṭat tiyalu meṉmaṉār pulavar.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/247/mode/1up">247</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/248/mode/1up">248</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēṟ cūttirattukkup puṟaṉaṭaiyāmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : koṭu eṉṟatu taṉmaikku ēṟṟataṉṟu, paṭarkkaikku uriyatōr collāyiṟṟu ; uyarntōṉ iḻintōṉai yirakkuṅkāl, tamaṉoruvaṉaik kāṭṭi, ivaṟkukkoṭu, eṉpatu ; āṇṭup paṭarkkaiyiṭattiṟku urittākak kūṟiṉāmaṉ ; āyiṉum, atu taṉmaiyiṭattē yiyalpu kāṭṭap paṭarkkaiyiṭattāṟku urittākātu avvirakkappaṭu poruḷum akkoṭu eṉṟa collum eṉpatu.</p>
<p>taṉṉaip piṟaṉpōṟ kūṟuṅ kuṟippil taṉṉaik koṭu eṉṟatu vāypāṭeṉṟatēṉum atu taṉakkē colliyavāṟu.</p>
<p>ummaiyāṟ piṟakiḷaviyum paṭarkkaiyāyiṉum taṉṉaip piṟaṉpōṟ kūṟuṅkuṟippiṟ ṟaṉṉiṭattu iyalum eṉṟavāṟu ; āṇṭu iraviṉkiḷavi yalvaḻi yeṉpatu. 'aṅṅaṉañ colluvāṉō peruñcāttaṉ tantai, collappaṭuvāḷō peruñ cāttaṉ tāy' eṉṉum taṉṉaip piṟaṉ pōlvāṉum; atu taṉṉiṭattu iyalum eṉṟavāṟu.	(52)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

